{"tid":1190355,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯不擔心擲汽油彈  被問約見法律界選委遭拒　斥對方擺款","createTime":"2019-06-07T09:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T10:27:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6aaae24bf9c0f0d2d761b5b7a7ca1f02140058","tid":1190355,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯表示，理解立法會加強保安，是鑑於近日氣氛緊張，批評有議員不守規矩，建立壞規矩。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否擔心凌晨在警察總部外懷疑投擲汽油彈事件，加上遊行臨近，會爆發衝突，他表示不擔心，亦相信警方的執法能力，會嚴肅調查汽油彈事件。<br />\n<br />\n對於30名法律界選委早前去信約見特首林鄭月娥商討修訂《逃犯條例》被拒，何君堯表示可惜，日前亦有以個人名義，邀請所有選委與他辯論；他表示特首事務繁忙，未必能會見選委，而自己身為議員有議事和考慮草案的職責，便向選委提供一個溝通的渠道，而選委卻指他未能代表特首和政府。他形容，法律界選委「擺款」，沒有作岀好好溝通，亦對法律界選委失望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461481-20190607.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461481-20190607.htm&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ur%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=6447500d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461481-20190607.htm&h=c698bb5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461481-20190607.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9c889a46f29ca95705c39e46fd51bf542e379b3a","tid":1190355,"uid":38521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"姐係話林鄭擺款啦"},{"pid":"129147b4f741335261b62b03c5991e3db20c22eb","tid":1190355,"uid":256056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccedb0bf043cf356d235f4852795218249022520","tid":1190355,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"豬隊友"},{"pid":"017f45aa86ca7025ba6fd9cb85e